Tool ID: red_cluster_alert_30min
Description: Shows any clusters in red status within the last 30 minutes, highlighting critical issues.
Labels: cluster-health
Configuration Type: ES|QL

ES|QL Query:

FROM .monitoring-es*
| WHERE type == "cluster_stats"
| WHERE timestamp >= NOW() - 30 MINUTES
| WHERE cluster_state.status == "red"
| STATS VALUES(cluster_state.status) BY timestamp
| SORT timestamp DESC
